         <Common_Consequences>
            <Consequence>
               <Scope>Availability</Scope>
               <Impact>DoS: Resource Consumption (Memory)</Impact>
               <Impact>DoS: Resource Consumption (Other)</Impact>
	       <Likelihood>High</Likelihood>
	       <Note>An adversary that can cause a resource counter to become inaccurate may be able to create situations where resources are not accounted for and not released, thus causing resources to become scarce for future needs.</Note>
            </Consequence>
            <Consequence>
               <Scope>Availability</Scope>
               <Impact>DoS: Crash, Exit, or Restart</Impact>
	       <Likelihood>Low</Likelihood>
	       <Note>An adversary that can cause a resource counter to become inaccurate may be able to force an error that causes the product to crash or exit out of its current operation.</Note>
            </Consequence>
         </Common_Consequences>
